          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p><fr:em>Forester</fr:em> is a tool for authoring, exploring, and sharing scientific and mathematical hypertexts. It is your lab notebook, your journal, your blackboard, and the home of your lecture notes.</fr:p>
